<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1936-09-25T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1936-09-25T14:00:00-05:00" n="457" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d457">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">851.5151/1025a: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Chargé in France</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-09-25T15:00:00-04:00">September
                                    25, 1936—3 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>370. From the Secretary of the Treasury for Cochran. I transmit to you
                            below our latest redraft<note n="36" xml:id="d457fn36">Not
                                printed.</note> of the proposed simultaneous declaration. You will
                            observe that the proposed revisions of the Anglo-French text submitted
                            to us are slight. Will you ascertain at once whether this draft is
                            acceptable to the French government and whether it will modify its draft
                            accordingly. We are giving a copy to the British Embassy in Washington
                            at once with the request that they ask the British the same
                            question.</p>
                        <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <list>
                                    <item>[Morgenthau]</item>
                                    <item>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                                    </item>
                                </list>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>